e-style-span&quot; style=&quot;color:#009900;font-family:Arial;font-size:14px;line-height:21px;&quot;&gt; 3. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;Apple-style-span&quot; style=&quot;color:#009900;font-family:Arial;font-size:14px;line-height:21px;&quot;&gt;Distributing our products through independent beauty and healthcare consultants who, working from home, beauty club, introduce, educate, and sell BTW wellness products locally through person-to-person and globally through professional team.&lt;/span&gt; \r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	&lt;span class=&quot;Apple-style-span&quot; style=&quot;color:#009900;font-family:Arial;font-size:14px;line-height:21px;&quot;&gt; 4. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;Apple-style-span&quot; style=&quot;color:#009900;font-family:Arial;font-size:14px;line-height:21px;&quot;&gt;Providing educational opportunities for all people interested in learning how BTW essential oils can be used as a self-care wellness alternative.&lt;/span&gt; \r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;\r\n	&lt;span class=&quot;Apple-style-span&quot; style=&quot;color:#009900;font-family:Arial;font-size:14px;line-height:21px;&quot;&gt; 5. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;Apple-style-span&quot; style=&quot;color:#009900;font-family:Arial;font-size:14px;line-height:21px;&quot;&gt;Bringing together healthcare professionals of traditional and alternative medicine to encourage further study and application of BTW essential oils in modern healthcare practices.&lt;/span&gt; \r\n&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;div style=&quot;font-size:12px;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;', null, 'en');
