 \\\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:smarttags\\\" /><st1:place w:st=\\\"on\\\">Rosa</st1:place> damascena)</i><?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = \\\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office\\\" /><o:p></o:p></span>\r\n</p>', '2011-11-26 15:33:35', '', 'en', 'BD012');
INSERT INTO `product` VALUES ('24', 'Jasmine     10ml     BD003', 'images/product/20111126191849653.jpg', null, null, '63', '<p style=\\\"margin:0cm 0cm 7.5pt;\\\">\r\n	<span style=\\\"font-family:Arial;background:white;color:#221f1f;font-size:9pt;\\\" lang=\\\"EN-US\\\">Jasmine** (Jasminum officinale) has a warm, exotic, floral fragrance that relaxes, soothes, uplifts, and enhances self-confidence. Jasmine is beneficial for the skin. It has been used throughout history for romance and attraction and for balancing the feminine energy of the body.<?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = \\\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office\\\" /><o:p></o:p></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\\\"margin:0cm 0cm 7.5pt;\\\">\r\n	<span style=\\\"font-family:Arial;background:white;color:#221f1f;font-size:9pt;\\\" lang=\\\"EN-US\\\">**Jasmine is an absolute or essence, rather than an essential oil.<o:p></o:p></span>\r\n</p>', '<p style=\\\"margin:0cm 0cm 7.5pt;\\\">\r\n	<span style=\\\"font-family:Arial;background:white;color:#221f1f;font-size:9pt;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold;\\\" lang=\\\"EN-US\\\">Directions:</span><span class=\\\"apple-converted-space\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Arial;background:white;color:#221f1f;font-size:9pt;\\\" lang=\\\"EN-US\\\">&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\\\"font-family:Arial;background:white;color:#221f1f;font-size:9pt;\\\" lang=\\\"EN-US\\\">Topical: Apply 2-4 drops directly to desired area. Dilution not required, except for the most sensitive skin. Use as needed. Aromatic: Diffuse up to 1 hour three times daily.<?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = \\\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office\\\" /><o:p></o:p></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\\\"margin:0cm 0cm 7.5pt;\\\">\r\n	<span style=\\\"font-family:Arial;background:white;color:#221f1f;font-size:9pt;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold;\\\" lang=\\\"EN-US\\\">Caution:</span><span class=\\\"apple-converted-space\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Arial;background:white;color:#221f1f;font-size:9pt;\\\" lang=\\\"EN-US\\\">&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\\\"font-family:Arial;background:white;color:#221f1f;font-size:9pt;\\\" lang=\\\"EN-US\\\">Keep out of reach of children. If pregnant, nursing, taking medication, or have a medical condition, consult a healthcare practioner prior to use.<o:p></o:p></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\\\"margin:0cm 0cm 7.5pt;\\\">\r\n	<span style=\\\"font-family:Arial;background:white;color:#221f1f;font-size:9pt;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold;\\\" lang=\\\"EN-US\\\">Storage:</span><span class=\\\"apple-converted-space\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Arial;background:white;color:#221f1f;font-size:9pt;\\\" lang=\\\"EN-US\\\">&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\\\"font-family:Arial;background:white;color:#221f1f;font-size:9pt;\\\" lang=\\\"EN-US\\\">Keep in a cool dark place<o:p></o:p></span>\r\n</p>', '<p style=\\\"margin:0cm 0cm 7.5pt;\\\">\r\n	<span style=\\\"font-family:Arial;background:white;color:#221f1f;font-size:9pt;\\\" lang=\\\"EN-US\\\">BTW 100% Pure Natural Organic Essential oil <span style=\\\"mso-spacerun:yes;\\\">&nbsp;</span><i>(J<span class=\\\"apple-style-span\\\">asminum officinale)</span></i><?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = \\\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office\\\" /><o:p></o:p></span>\r\n</p>', '2011-11-26 19:17:37', '', 'en', 'BD003');
INSERT INTO `product` VALUES ('25', 'Geranium     10ml     BD019', 'images/product/20111126192809137.jpg', null, null, '63', '<p style=\\\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;\\\" class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\">\r\n	<span class=\\\"apple-style-span\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Arial;background:white;color:#221f1f;font-size:9pt;\\\" lang=\\\"EN-US\\\">Geranium (Pelargonium graveolens) has a wonderfully uplifting, calming, flowery scent. It is excellent for the skin, and its aromatic influence helps release negative memories. Used traditionally to support the circulatory and nervous systems, a great deal of its strength lies in its ability to revitalize body tissues.* Geranium has an approximate ORAC of 1,010,011 (TE/L). TE/L is expressed as micromole Trolox equivalent per liter.<?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = \\\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office\\\" /><o:p></o:p></span></span>\r\n</p>', '<p style=\\\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;\\\" class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\">\r\n	<span class=\\\"apple-style-span\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Arial;background:white;color:#221f1f;font-size:9pt;\\\" lang=\\\"EN-US\\\">Geranium (Pelargonium graveolens) has a wonderfully uplifting, calming, flowery scent. It is excellent for the skin, and its aromatic influence helps release negative memories. Used traditionally to support the circulatory and nervous systems, a great deal of its strength lies in its ability to revitalize body tissues.* Geranium has an approximate ORAC of 1,010,011 (TE/L). TE/L is expressed as micromole Trolox equivalent per liter.</span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<span class=\\\"apple-style-span\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Arial;background:white;color:#221f1f;font-size:9pt;\\\" lang=\\\"EN-US\\\"> \r\n<p style=\\\"margin:0cm 0cm 7.5pt;\\\">\r\n	<b><span style=\\\"font-family:Arial;background:white;color:#221f1f;font-size:9pt;\\\" lang=\\\"EN-US\\\">Storage:</span></b><span class=\\\"apple-converted-space\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:Arial;background:white;color:#221f1f;font-size:9pt;\\\" lang=\\